Interface MethodIfc

All Superinterfaces:
java.lang.Comparable
All Known Implementing Classes:
MethodImpl, MethodImpl
public interface MethodIfc
extends java.lang.Comparable

MethodIfc.java defines method abstract object. As methods I mean functions, constructors and procedures. Through implementation of this interface you should be able to access all method parameters such as:

  1. Method name
  2. List of method parameters
  3. Method return type
  4. List of exceptions throw by this method
  5. Method visibility
